item.title: Data Science Studio
item.description: DSS is a learning community for applied researchers in the areas of health and aging. Based at the Institute for Aging and Lifelong Health (IALH) at the University of Victoria, DSS provides a learning space and a platform for cross-disciplinary dialog between UVic researchers and Vancouver Island Health Authority.
